WEBVTT

00:06.377 --> 00:09.541
<i>Air and naval forces</i>
<i>of the United States</i>

00:09.575 --> 00:12.373
<i>launched a series of strikes</i>
<i>against terrorist facilities...</i>

00:12.407 --> 00:14.505
<i>Pan Am Flight 103 crashed</i>
<i>into the the town of Lockerbie.</i>

00:14.540 --> 00:15.872
<i>...savage acts of terror in</i>

00:15.906 --> 00:18.509
<i>Africa, Europe,</i>
<i>the Middle East.</i>

00:18.543 --> 00:21.348
<i>This will not stand, this</i>
<i>aggression against, uh, Kuwait.</i>

00:21.383 --> 00:22.915
- <i>- This relentless pursuit of terror.</i>

00:22.949 --> 00:24.682
<i>We will make no distinction.</i>

00:24.717 --> 00:26.014
<i>The USS</i> Cole <i>was attacked</i>

00:26.049 --> 00:27.215
<i>while refueling in</i>
<i>the port of Aden.</i>

00:27.249 --> 00:29.182
This was an act of terrorism.

00:29.216 --> 00:31.682
It was a despicable
and cowardly act.

00:32.075 --> 00:34.375
<i>The next song</i>
<i>we're going to play for you</i>

00:34.409 --> 00:35.542
is one of the good old
favorites.

00:35.576 --> 00:38.175
...until something stops him.

00:38.209 --> 00:41.008
<i>I'm just making sure</i>
<i>we don't get hit again.</i>

00:41.042 --> 00:44.576
<i>That plane crashed</i>
<i>into the World Trade Center.</i>

00:45.942 --> 00:48.242
<i>Thousands of people running.</i>

00:48.275 --> 00:52.733
We must and we will remain
vigilant at home and abroad.

00:58.576 --> 01:01.042
<i>What the fuck are you doing?</i>

01:01.075 --> 01:02.058
God!

01:02.178 --> 01:03.792
<i>Fuck! I missed</i>
<i>something once before.</i>

01:04.053 --> 01:06.968
<i>I won't...</i>
<i>I</i> can't <i>let that happen again.</i>

01:09.160 --> 01:10.577
<i>It was ten years ago.</i>

01:10.696 --> 01:12.329
<i>Everyone missed something</i>
<i>that day.</i>

01:12.363 --> 01:14.329
<i>Everyone's not me.</i>

01:15.224 --> 01:22.878
<font color="#ec14bd">Sync & corrected by honeybunny</font>
<font color="#ec14bd">www.addic7ed.com</font>

01:24.730 --> 01:26.663
<i>Previously on</i> Homeland:

01:26.696 --> 01:28.196
How has the homecoming been?

01:28.229 --> 01:29.363
It's been great.

01:29.396 --> 01:31.796
For all of us.

01:31.830 --> 01:35.229
<i>I appreciate you</i>
<i>looking out for Jessica,</i>

01:35.263 --> 01:37.796
like you did while I was gone.

01:37.830 --> 01:38.830
What do you want to know?

01:38.863 --> 01:40.730
How he died.

01:40.763 --> 01:42.897
<i>He's gone.</i>

01:42.930 --> 01:44.329
Does it really matter
how it happened?

01:44.363 --> 01:45.730
It does to me.

01:45.763 --> 01:48.029
We're onto the next case.

01:48.062 --> 01:49.563
Raqim Faisel.

01:49.596 --> 01:51.162
What did you say?

01:51.196 --> 01:53.596
He should use an alternate
route. Tell him now.

01:56.963 --> 01:59.062
<i>See what second team</i>

01:59.096 --> 02:00.162
comes up with tonight.

02:00.196 --> 02:01.263
If nothing, move on.

02:02.296 --> 02:04.162
What?

02:04.196 --> 02:05.663
The one surviving terrorist

02:05.696 --> 02:06.930
<i>from the compound</i>
<i>in Afghanistan</i>

02:06.963 --> 02:08.229
<i>where we rescued Brody.</i>

02:08.263 --> 02:09.530
<i>Scooped him up in</i>

02:09.562 --> 02:10.997
<i>some shit shack in IBD.</i>

02:11.029 --> 02:12.429
<i>Afzal Hamid.</i>

02:12.463 --> 02:13.930
You and Carrie
will interrogate him,

02:13.963 --> 02:15.396
<i>with the help</i>
<i>of Sergeant Brody.</i>

02:15.429 --> 02:16.997
Do you know this man?

02:17.029 --> 02:20.229
He was my guard.

02:20.263 --> 02:21.830
What can I do for you, Sergeant?

02:21.863 --> 02:23.029
I believe I've earned
a moment face-to-face

02:23.062 --> 02:25.096
<i>with my torturer, sir.</i>

02:29.129 --> 02:31.062
14th man gave up
an e-mail address we just traced

02:31.096 --> 02:33.263
to the Engineering Department
at Bryden University.

02:33.296 --> 02:34.963
Professor we tailed then cleared?
Correct.

02:34.997 --> 02:36.129
Find this man.

02:36.162 --> 02:37.463
Raqim Faisel.

02:37.496 --> 02:40.229
What's going on, Saul?

02:40.263 --> 02:43.129
Hamid's dead.

02:43.162 --> 02:44.429
Suicide.

02:44.463 --> 02:46.363
How the hell is that possible?

02:46.396 --> 02:48.029
Razor blade fragment.

02:48.062 --> 02:49.563
Left wrist.

02:49.596 --> 02:51.630
What? Where did he get that?

02:51.663 --> 02:54.897
What the hell?

02:54.930 --> 02:57.196
Not only did Brody contrive
to get himself in the room,

02:57.229 --> 02:59.796
he orchestrated Hamid's suicide
and he warned Dr. Faisel.

02:59.830 --> 03:02.429
And we-- you and I--
let it happen.

03:02.463 --> 03:04.897
I think you should leave now.

03:04.930 --> 03:06.263
With pleasure.

03:06.296 --> 03:07.463
Know what, you can keep that.

03:07.496 --> 03:08.663
Fuck this shit!

