contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

03:22.263 --> 03:23.796
How did you think this...

03:27.096 --> 03:28.997
Come on!

03:30.296 --> 03:31.997
Come on!

03:34.196 --> 03:35.229
Come on!

03:49.563 --> 03:50.530
Calm down!

03:50.563 --> 03:53.029
Calm down. Calm down.

03:53.062 --> 03:55.930
How is such a massive
fuck-up even possible?

03:55.963 --> 03:57.930
Please, explain that to me.

03:57.963 --> 03:59.830
Sorry I'm late.

03:59.863 --> 04:01.463
Hamid probably brought
the razor blade with him.

04:01.496 --> 04:03.663
The heel of one of his
shoes was peeled back.

04:03.696 --> 04:04.963
It's also conceivable that
he found the razor blade

04:04.997 --> 04:06.429
somewhere in the safe house.

04:06.463 --> 04:08.963
One of our sweepers
might have missed it.

04:08.997 --> 04:10.897
There is another possibility.

04:12.596 --> 04:15.296
Someone on our side
could have given it to him.

04:15.329 --> 04:16.997
Th-That's a stretch.

04:17.029 --> 04:18.663
Why?

04:18.696 --> 04:20.363
You actually think
someone on the SEAL team

04:20.396 --> 04:21.997
gave Hamid a piece
of broken razor blade?

04:22.029 --> 04:23.730
Or maybe you think
I did it, or Saul.

04:23.763 --> 04:25.129
I certainly don't
think you did it.

04:25.162 --> 04:26.563
I'm just saying, we
should polygraph

04:26.596 --> 04:28.730
everyone who came into
contact with Hamid.

04:28.763 --> 04:31.663
Ask each one of them directly
about the razor blade.

04:31.696 --> 04:33.229
I've written up a list.

04:33.263 --> 04:35.029
We're talking about 11 people,

04:35.062 --> 04:36.963
including the SEAL team
that brought him here.

04:36.997 --> 04:38.963
She's right.

04:38.997 --> 04:40.830
We can't rule out
the possibility

04:40.863 --> 04:42.763
of a mole.

04:42.796 --> 04:45.763
What if Raqim Faisel
was warned by the same person

04:45.796 --> 04:46.930
who gave Hamid the razor blade?

04:46.963 --> 04:48.329
Faisel?

04:48.363 --> 04:50.363
The guy that bought the house
by the airport?

04:50.396 --> 04:51.997
You want to connect him to this?

04:52.029 --> 04:54.596
He disappeared
just as we moved in.

04:54.630 --> 04:55.863
Coincidence?

04:55.897 --> 04:57.863
Or did he know we were coming?

04:57.897 --> 05:01.329
Oh, good Christ.

05:01.363 --> 05:04.329
Look, if nothing more,
let's cover our asses.

05:04.363 --> 05:06.696
11 polygraph tests.
What's the big deal?

05:06.730 --> 05:08.863
I'll go first.

05:12.396 --> 05:15.897
Take care of the polygraphs.

05:22.029 --> 05:23.630
Don't you ever do
that to me again!

05:23.663 --> 05:26.730
You disagree with me, fine,
but make it a sidebar!

05:29.830 --> 05:31.563
Well, you heard
what the man said.

05:31.596 --> 05:32.663
Set up the polygraphs!

05:32.696 --> 05:34.396
And get me Faisel!

05:34.429 --> 05:36.429
Yes, sir.

05:43.997 --> 05:46.029
What a surprise.
Sergeant Brody's on this list.

05:46.062 --> 05:47.229
Well, it's not my fault

05:47.263 --> 05:48.830
Estes let him in
the room with Hamid.

05:48.863 --> 05:49.963
Expected to find
your resignation

05:49.997 --> 05:51.496
on my desk this morning.

05:51.530 --> 05:53.062
I had a much better
idea, don't you think?

05:53.096 --> 05:54.263
I should forget
the things you said?

05:54.296 --> 05:55.563
Yes, please.

05:57.429 --> 05:59.096
He's right, you know.

05:59.129 --> 06:00.463
You embarrassed him in there.

06:00.496 --> 06:01.997
Who gives a shit?

06:02.029 --> 06:04.329
Saul, we're gonna get Brody.

06:04.363 --> 06:06.830
He'll never pass
the polygraph test.

06:06.863 --> 06:08.229
We'll see.

06:08.263 --> 06:09.930
I'll bet you
everything I've got.

06:09.963 --> 06:12.096
Everything. Including
my <i>Monk's Dream,</i>

06:12.129 --> 06:14.263
signed by Thelonious himself.

06:14.296 --> 06:15.730
I prefer Coltrane.

06:15.763 --> 06:18.496
Not so fussy.

06:31.763 --> 06:34.229
Okay, uh, here.

06:34.263 --> 06:36.263
So, uh, the tables
will go right here,

06:36.296 --> 06:37.496
the chairs around the tables,

06:37.530 --> 06:39.563
and then just
throughout the yard, okay?

06:39.596 --> 06:41.329
All right.

06:43.396 --> 06:45.530
Yeah, okay.

06:47.263 --> 06:48.630
Damn it you two.

06:48.663 --> 06:50.563
The memorial
is in a half an hour.

06:50.596 --> 06:53.263
You're supposed to be ready.
Get dressed.

06:53.296 --> 06:55.530
Ma, this little creep
keeps hogging the bathroom!

06:55.563 --> 06:56.630
Chris, let your sister

06:56.663 --> 06:57.897
use the bathroom, please!

06:59.530 --> 07:01.029
You okay?

07:01.062 --> 07:05.296
Not exactly looking forward
to seeing Helen Walker.

07:05.329 --> 07:08.329
Kind of got on my high horse
when she remarried.

07:08.363 --> 07:10.196
Why?

07:10.229 --> 07:12.196
I was waiting for you
to come home.

07:12.229 --> 07:14.830
I guess I figured
she could do the same.

07:14.863 --> 07:16.463
I had no right.

07:18.496 --> 07:20.930
Do you know
what you're going to say?

07:20.963 --> 07:22.096
At the service?

07:24.029 --> 07:25.830
No.

07:25.863 --> 07:27.463
Well, just be honest.

07:27.496 --> 07:30.396
I'm sure everything's
gonna be fine.

07:35.830 --> 07:37.830
We should hurry.

07:45.496 --> 07:47.463
Here.

08:04.596 --> 08:06.162
You look very handsome,

08:06.196 --> 08:08.196
Sergeant Brody.

08:27.396 --> 08:29.329
Is your name
Carrie Mathison?

08:29.363 --> 08:30.696
Last time I checked.

08:30.730 --> 08:32.029
Yes or no, please.

08:32.062 --> 08:33.763
Yes.

08:33.796 --> 08:35.596
Do you work for
the Central Intelligence Agency?

08:35.630 --> 08:37.062
Yes.

08:37.096 --> 08:39.563
Regarding the questions
you'll be asked today,

08:39.596 --> 08:41.129
do you intend
to tell the truth?

08:41.162 --> 08:42.129
Yes.

08:42.162 --> 08:44.029
Are you married?

08:44.062 --> 08:45.796
No.

08:45.830 --> 08:47.696
Have you ever been married?

08:47.730 --> 08:49.129
No.

08:49.162 --> 08:50.796
Do you have children?

08:50.830 --> 08:52.196
No.

08:52.229 --> 08:54.897
Did you ever commit
a minor traffic violation?

08:54.930 --> 08:57.463
Yes.

08:57.496 --> 08:58.963
Are you now in Mississippi?

08:58.997 --> 09:00.863
No.

09:00.897 --> 09:03.429
Have you ever revealed
any classified information

09:03.463 --> 09:05.630
to anyone without
proper security clearance?

09:05.663 --> 09:07.229
No.

09:07.263 --> 09:09.596
Have you ever taken
any illegal drugs?

09:10.663 --> 09:13.329
Yes.

09:13.363 --> 09:15.296
Have you taken
any illegal drugs

09:15.329 --> 09:17.796
since joining
the Central Intelligence Agency?

09:17.830 --> 09:19.696
No.

09:23.696 --> 09:26.096
Did you pass a razor blade
to Afzal Hamid?

09:26.129 --> 09:27.963
No.

09:41.129 --> 09:43.796
Okay.

09:43.830 --> 09:45.229
Here we go.

09:49.663 --> 09:51.696
All ready, sir?

09:55.296 --> 09:59.129
Um, is your name David Estes?

09:59.162 --> 10:01.663
Yes.

10:01.696 --> 10:05.096
Do you work for the Central
Intelligence Agency?

10:05.129 --> 10:06.263
Yes.

10:06.296 --> 10:08.296
Are you married?

10:08.329 --> 10:10.963
You know, I was married,
but I cheated on her,

10:10.997 --> 10:12.696
so that kind of soured things.

10:15.029 --> 10:17.162
Is that a no?

10:19.229 --> 10:21.329
No.

10:23.363 --> 10:25.363
No. Okay.

10:25.396 --> 10:27.730
Uh, do you have children?

10:27.763 --> 10:29.563
Yes.

10:29.596 --> 10:32.229
Not that they're talking to me.

10:32.263 --> 10:35.863
Did you pass a razor blade
to Afzal Hamid?

10:35.897 --> 10:37.329
No.

10:46.530 --> 10:48.229
Find anything?

10:48.263 --> 10:49.696
Eight million fingerprints,

10:49.730 --> 10:51.930
a man's belt from Macy's--
size 32--

10:51.963 --> 10:53.496
couple of takeout
food containers

10:53.530 --> 10:55.263
from a local
Chinese restaurant.

10:55.296 --> 10:56.496
Condoms.

10:56.530 --> 10:58.596
Condoms? What else?

10:58.630 --> 11:00.997
A six-pack of diet Coke
in the refrigerator.

11:02.263 --> 11:04.196
That's it?

11:04.229 --> 11:06.196
Interview the neighbors?

11:06.229 --> 11:08.563
In progress.

11:08.596 --> 11:09.997
Her?

11:10.029 --> 11:13.429
Not yet.

11:17.596 --> 11:19.596
I apologize for all
the commotion, ma'am.

11:19.630 --> 11:21.196
We'll be out of your hair soon.

11:21.229 --> 11:22.730
Oh, this is very exciting.

11:22.763 --> 11:24.963
It's not often we get
a murderer living

11:24.997 --> 11:27.263
in the neighborhood.
Murderer?

11:27.296 --> 11:29.363
That's what Marilyn
across the street said--

11:29.396 --> 11:30.696
a cold-blooded murderer

11:30.730 --> 11:32.630
raped and strangled
some poor girl

11:32.663 --> 11:35.696
over in Fairfax County.
Whew! Lock your doors tight tonight.

11:35.730 --> 11:37.730
Oh, I will.

11:39.062 --> 11:41.530
Mr. Jawdal moved in
about, uh...

11:41.563 --> 11:44.296
three weeks ago?
That's right.

11:44.329 --> 11:46.363
Anything you can tell me
about him?

11:46.396 --> 11:49.363
He was very quiet and polite.

11:49.396 --> 11:51.596
They pretty much
kept to themselves.

11:51.630 --> 11:53.229
They?

11:53.263 --> 11:55.296
He and his wife.

11:57.530 --> 11:59.930
- What happened? - I don't know. Someone must
have found out about the house.

11:59.963 --> 12:00.930
How?
I don't know.

12:00.963 --> 12:01.930
Where are we going?

12:01.963 --> 12:04.897
Someplace safe.
Says who?

12:04.930 --> 12:07.296
This is nuts.

12:08.363 --> 12:09.596
There's no one there.

12:09.630 --> 12:10.997
Yeah? How do you know?

12:11.029 --> 12:12.329
I know. Relax, okay?

12:12.363 --> 12:13.930
We're fine.
Fine?

12:13.963 --> 12:15.730
Are you kidding me?
We're not fine.

12:15.763 --> 12:16.830
We're fucked!

12:26.096 --> 12:28.196
Raqim?
What?

12:30.796 --> 12:33.129
I'm sorry I dragged
you into this.

12:36.329 --> 12:39.429
You didn't drag me into it.

12:39.463 --> 12:41.196
Okay?

12:41.229 --> 12:43.863
I dragged myself into it.

12:46.730 --> 12:50.496
I am a victim of
your fabulousness.

12:52.830 --> 12:54.496
Are you saying I'm fabulous?

12:54.530 --> 12:56.696
Yes, I am.

12:56.730 --> 12:58.897
You are so full of shit.

13:07.363 --> 13:11.363
<i>I asked all of you
here</i> <i>today to help me</i>

13:11.396 --> 13:15.296
say good-bye
to my former husband,

13:15.329 --> 13:17.329
Tom Walker.

13:21.530 --> 13:23.630
This has been a...

13:23.663 --> 13:25.863
very difficult...

13:25.897 --> 13:27.863
eight years.

13:30.263 --> 13:32.663
And now finally we can...

13:32.696 --> 13:36.596
give Tom the farewell
he deserves.

13:45.329 --> 13:49.029
Tom, uh, always said
that Nick Brody

13:49.062 --> 13:51.162
was his closest friend.

13:51.196 --> 13:53.162
And Nick was with Tom

13:53.196 --> 13:55.496
when he died.

13:56.596 --> 13:58.696
Nick.

14:31.463 --> 14:33.796
Tom Walker was a good man.

14:37.162 --> 14:39.830
A true Marine...

14:39.863 --> 14:42.596
and the best shot
I ever encountered, bar n...

14:42.630 --> 14:43.796
Sorry.

14:49.229 --> 14:50.596
Sorry.

15:01.263 --> 15:03.796
Tom was the opposite
of pretentious,

15:03.830 --> 15:05.596
whatever <i>that</i> is.

15:05.630 --> 15:08.530
Humble?

15:08.563 --> 15:13.029
He just wanted to get the job
done and get back to his family.

15:39.596 --> 15:41.796
Staff Sergeant Calhoun?

15:48.062 --> 15:49.263
Present!

15:49.296 --> 15:50.463
Private First Class

15:50.496 --> 15:51.630
Fernandez?

15:53.162 --> 15:54.296
Present!

15:54.329 --> 15:56.429
Private First Class Wakefield?

15:58.029 --> 15:59.463
Present.

15:59.496 --> 16:00.663
Captain Faber?

16:00.696 --> 16:02.429
Present!

16:02.463 --> 16:04.696
Private First Class Green?

16:04.730 --> 16:06.763
Present.

16:06.796 --> 16:09.229
Corporal Walker?

16:14.162 --> 16:17.630
Corporal Thomas Walker?

16:23.096 --> 16:25.296
Corporal Thomas...

16:25.329 --> 16:28.162
Patrick...

16:28.196 --> 16:30.696
Walker.

16:55.096 --> 16:57.429
Good service.
Yeah, it was really good.

16:57.463 --> 16:59.229
Will you excuse me?

16:59.263 --> 17:01.396
I'll be back in a minute, all right?
Mm-hmm.

17:01.429 --> 17:02.796
Okay.
Okay? All right.

17:15.930 --> 17:17.363
Sergeant Brody?

17:17.396 --> 17:18.530
Yeah?

17:18.563 --> 17:21.363
Hey. That must
have been hard.

17:21.396 --> 17:22.663
Yeah.

17:22.695 --> 17:24.563
Hey, I hate to do
this right now,

17:24.596 --> 17:25.730
but my bosses

17:25.762 --> 17:27.363
kind of insist.

17:27.396 --> 17:31.062
We need you to come out to
Langley to take a polygraph.

17:31.096 --> 17:32.530
Why?

17:32.563 --> 17:34.796
I'm afraid that's classified.

17:34.830 --> 17:36.429
Can you come out today?

17:36.463 --> 17:38.363
Is this to do with Hamid?

17:38.396 --> 17:40.763
I can't say.
I'm sorry.

17:42.062 --> 17:44.463
Well, I got to go
back to the reception.

17:44.496 --> 17:46.263
They're having it at my house.

17:46.296 --> 17:47.696
Oh, um...

17:47.730 --> 17:49.129
how about tomorrow?

17:49.162 --> 17:51.263
10:00 a.m.?

17:51.296 --> 17:52.596
Okay.

17:52.630 --> 17:55.162
Okay.

18:06.997 --> 18:09.429
Faisel's got a woman with him--
maybe a girlfriend,

18:09.463 --> 18:11.263
maybe a wife,
maybe just a cohort.

18:11.296 --> 18:12.329
She's Caucasian,
mid-20s,

18:12.363 --> 18:13.496
blond hair, blue/green eyes,

18:13.530 --> 18:14.963
depending who you talk to.

18:14.997 --> 18:17.329
Caucasian?
Yep.

18:17.363 --> 18:19.496
What do we know about her?
Nothing.

18:19.530 --> 18:20.830
We lifted a bunch
of fingerprints

18:20.863 --> 18:22.630
from the house--
we're hoping at least

18:22.663 --> 18:25.062
one of them will be hers and that we'll
be able to I.D. her.

18:25.096 --> 18:27.263
Hey, can we change gears
for a second?

