Oh, I hope I don't puke.

36:12.129 --> 36:13.363
You're gonna puke?

36:13.396 --> 36:15.096
No.
You all right?

36:15.129 --> 36:17.530
I'm half Irish.
The Irish don't puke?

36:17.563 --> 36:20.696
Nah, only when we have
to salute the British.

36:29.329 --> 36:31.696
This is me.

36:37.263 --> 36:39.263
Want to know
what it's all about?

36:39.296 --> 36:40.930
The polygraph?

36:40.963 --> 36:42.930
I thought that was classified.

36:42.963 --> 36:44.796
It is.

36:44.830 --> 36:48.229
Hamid's dead.

36:48.263 --> 36:51.129
Someone slipped him
a razorblade in the safe house.

36:51.162 --> 36:53.530
Slit his wrists.

36:56.162 --> 36:58.830
So...

37:56.162 --> 37:58.496
♪ Will I ever catch a break?

37:58.530 --> 38:01.396
♪ That's when I remember

38:01.429 --> 38:04.530
♪ He's the one
I have to fake 'cause I got... ♪

38:04.563 --> 38:08.196
Any more secrets
you want to share, huh?

38:08.229 --> 38:09.596
What else don't I know?

38:09.630 --> 38:11.229
Can't hear the song.

38:11.263 --> 38:12.696
How can you just sit there
listening to wailing cowboys

38:12.730 --> 38:14.496
when our lives
are falling apart?

38:14.530 --> 38:16.363
I need to relax. I can't think
straight if I don't relax.

38:16.396 --> 38:18.730
No, what we need
is a fucking plan.

38:18.763 --> 38:21.429
What if we went to Mexico?

38:21.463 --> 38:24.429
No. We should turn ourselves in.
No.

38:24.463 --> 38:26.062
Yes, we can ask for
protective custody.

38:26.096 --> 38:27.730
I'd rather die.

38:27.763 --> 38:29.530
♪ Don't sweat
the little things... ♪

38:29.563 --> 38:32.129
Yeah? Well, you're going to.

38:39.496 --> 38:41.863
I got to pee.

38:41.897 --> 38:45.263
♪ And pulled out a .45

38:45.296 --> 38:48.463
♪ Well, that's when
people started to scramble ♪

38:48.496 --> 38:50.296
♪ I saw a child in the front

38:51.863 --> 38:54.530
♪ Without thought,
I told the children ♪

38:54.563 --> 38:56.730
♪ As the stranger fired
his gun ♪

38:56.763 --> 39:00.630
♪ And I thought, Lord,
I thank you... ♪

39:37.696 --> 39:40.563
You're awake.

39:40.596 --> 39:42.663
Jet lag, I guess.

39:42.696 --> 39:44.196
I got some good news.

39:44.229 --> 39:46.897
Hmm. Do you want some tea?

39:46.930 --> 39:48.730
Tea? Sure.

39:48.763 --> 39:50.696
Thanks.

39:50.730 --> 39:52.897
Oh.

39:52.930 --> 39:56.863
I've put in
for the New Delhi station.

39:56.897 --> 40:01.062
Ed Welles retires
in a few months.

40:01.096 --> 40:04.096
I believe
I've got Estes' backing.

40:04.129 --> 40:06.429
Take the new job.

40:06.463 --> 40:08.463
I can come with you.

40:10.897 --> 40:13.296
I don't want you
to come with me.

40:13.329 --> 40:15.563
What?

40:15.596 --> 40:17.396
I want to go alone.

40:17.429 --> 40:20.129
I <i>need</i> to go alone.

40:20.162 --> 40:22.663
Why?

40:22.696 --> 40:25.096
I just do.

40:27.263 --> 40:28.830
For how long?

40:28.863 --> 40:32.296
I-I don't know.

40:32.329 --> 40:33.830
A week?

40:33.863 --> 40:36.329
I don't know.

40:36.363 --> 40:39.229
A month?

40:39.263 --> 40:41.463
What?

40:41.496 --> 40:43.830
I don't know.

40:48.796 --> 40:51.530
New job?

40:51.563 --> 40:54.162
Just a ploy?

40:54.196 --> 40:56.930
Your way
of letting me down gently?

40:56.963 --> 40:59.329
Saul...

40:59.363 --> 41:03.463
we're like good friends
sharing a house.

41:03.496 --> 41:06.463
You do the dishes,
I water the garden.

41:06.496 --> 41:09.930
You are watching football,
I watch cooking shows.

41:09.963 --> 41:12.830
You play golf, I do yoga.

41:17.329 --> 41:20.530
Sounds perfect.

41:47.162 --> 41:49.796
Come on. We're late.

41:51.863 --> 41:54.263
Come on.

41:59.763 --> 42:02.196
Have a good day at school,
sugar bunny.

42:03.429 --> 42:05.830
Right.

42:05.863 --> 42:07.997
Dana.

42:25.830 --> 42:27.663
Did you go to college?

42:27.696 --> 42:29.363
Yes.

42:29.396 --> 42:31.329
Did you major
in Political Science?

42:31.363 --> 42:33.229
Yes.

42:33.263 --> 42:37.930
Have you ever sold secrets
to an agent of another country?

42:37.963 --> 42:39.396
No.

42:39.429 --> 42:40.830
Are you married?

42:40.863 --> 42:44.663
No, not really.

42:45.897 --> 42:48.596
Yes or no?

42:51.029 --> 42:53.396
I don't know, Larry.

42:54.630 --> 42:57.229
Okay?

42:57.263 --> 42:59.830
Maybe yes, maybe no.

42:59.863 --> 43:01.229
Technically?

43:01.263 --> 43:04.229
Technically, yes.

43:04.263 --> 43:07.696
Did you give

43:07.730 --> 43:10.029
Afzal Hamid a razorblade?

43:10.062 --> 43:12.429
No.

43:13.663 --> 43:16.029
That's it.

43:16.062 --> 43:18.396
You're free.

43:18.429 --> 43:20.129
Oh.

43:24.496 --> 43:26.863
I hope I never see you again.

43:26.897 --> 43:28.796
Oh, you will.

43:28.830 --> 43:31.229
Thanks, buddy.

43:45.596 --> 43:47.563
Trouble at home.

43:47.596 --> 43:49.463
It'll blow over.

43:49.496 --> 43:51.096
Brody next?

43:51.129 --> 43:53.129
Brody's next.

43:53.162 --> 43:54.897
Assuming he shows up.

43:54.930 --> 43:56.596
This is it, Saul.

43:56.630 --> 43:58.463
Finally.

43:58.496 --> 43:59.930
Let's hope.

44:25.129 --> 44:26.997
Come on in,
Sergeant Brody.

44:27.029 --> 44:28.496
Just stand over here.

44:28.530 --> 44:29.997
This won't take long.

44:30.029 --> 44:31.997
Can you just, uh,
take your jacket off?

44:32.029 --> 44:34.630
You can put it on
the chair there.

44:40.997 --> 44:42.363
Oh...

44:55.730 --> 44:56.997
Okay.

44:57.029 --> 45:00.062
Now, just relax

45:00.096 --> 45:02.863
and answer all the questions

45:02.897 --> 45:06.396
honestly, yes or no.

45:06.429 --> 45:07.863
All set?
Mm-hmm.

45:07.897 --> 45:09.897
Okay.

45:09.930 --> 45:13.129
Is your name Nicholas Brody?

45:13.162 --> 45:14.696
Yes.

45:14.730 --> 45:17.263
Are you a member
of the U.S. Marine Corps?

45:17.296 --> 45:18.596
Yes.

45:18.630 --> 45:21.096
Do you intend
to tell the truth here today?

45:21.129 --> 45:22.930
Yes.

45:22.963 --> 45:25.429
Have you ever sold secrets
to a foreign government?

45:25.463 --> 45:27.062
No.

45:27.096 --> 45:29.229
Have you
ever been arrested?

45:29.263 --> 45:33.396
- Yes.
- I borrowed my dad's Pontiac one time.

45:33.429 --> 45:35.229
I was 15 years old.

45:35.263 --> 45:38.596
Have you ever been
arrested for a felony?

45:38.630 --> 45:40.263
No.

45:40.296 --> 45:43.162
Have you ever killed a man?

45:43.196 --> 45:44.830
Yes.

45:44.863 --> 45:48.062
Did you pass Afzal Hamid
a razorblade?

45:48.096 --> 45:49.062
No.

45:49.096 --> 45:50.963
Do you live at

45:50.997 --> 45:52.796
3319 West Chapman Street?

45:52.830 --> 45:54.463
Yes.

45:54.496 --> 45:56.196
Are you
sometimes called Nick?

45:56.229 --> 45:58.196
Yes.

45:58.229 --> 46:00.096
Is Boston the
capital of Massachusetts?

46:00.129 --> 46:01.763
Yes.

46:01.796 --> 46:03.296
Do you know Afzal Hamid?

46:03.329 --> 46:04.730
Yes.

46:04.763 --> 46:06.463
Did you
meet him in Syria?

46:06.496 --> 46:08.596
Yes.

46:08.630 --> 46:10.396
Did you slip him a razorblade?

46:10.429 --> 46:12.196
No.

46:12.229 --> 46:14.563
Ask him again.

46:15.796 --> 46:17.763
Did you slip

46:17.796 --> 46:20.229
Afzal Hamid a razorblade?

46:20.263 --> 46:23.496
No.

46:26.329 --> 46:29.229
Ask him if he's ever been
unfaithful to his wife.

46:31.663 --> 46:34.630
Go on, ask him.

46:34.663 --> 46:38.363
Have you ever been
unfaithful to your wife?

46:41.096 --> 46:43.496
No.

46:47.162 --> 46:49.730
Okay, Larry, wrap it up.

46:49.763 --> 46:52.563
Thank you, Sergeant Brody.

46:52.596 --> 46:53.763
That it?
We all done?

46:53.796 --> 46:55.296
We're all done.

46:55.329 --> 46:56.830
He's lying.

46:56.863 --> 46:58.630
He passed the polygraph.

46:58.663 --> 47:01.029
Same one you and I take
and flub every time.

47:01.062 --> 47:02.463
Or at least I do.

47:04.630 --> 47:08.263
It's... It's over.

47:08.296 --> 47:10.196
Man is clean.

47:10.229 --> 47:12.663
Saul...

47:13.863 --> 47:17.630
You can't deny the facts--

47:17.663 --> 47:19.429
what we just
witnessed--

47:19.463 --> 47:21.663
just 'cause you find
them inconvenient.

47:27.296 --> 47:29.663
So...

47:29.696 --> 47:33.029
now we know

47:33.062 --> 47:36.029
that Sergeant Brody's
been faithful to his wife.

